snippet.title: Spirittea: Wholesome Snack Trailer (Coming to Game Pass, Switch and PC in 2023!)
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1931010/Spirittea/

This brand new trailer for Spirittea, shown for the first time during the Wholesome Snack 2022 Showcase, gives some insight into how your time with Spirittea will unfold!
